{"about_the_game":"Exostation is a sci-fi real-time strategy game. Reach sustainable planet economies by building, allocating, mining, and selling wisely. Allow humanity to spread and conquer new solar systems not by war but by ensuring its planet's resources are not exhausted.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1813120/extras/menu.gif?t=1675442150\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Help humanity become a multi-planetary species</h2><br>Earth is not the only planet humanity can live on anymore. A multi-planetary species means new planets to discover and develop.<br>As a space explorer, you will explore new solar systems, it will be your responsibility to build each planet's economy. Sustainability is the key!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1813120/extras/hq.gif?t=1675442150\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Build Exostations on new worlds</h2><br>Before growing the population of a new planet, fulfilling their basic needs is required. You will have to ensure there is enough food and water to feed them and enough shelter for them to survive. Build farms, water pumps, and housing.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1813120/extras/night.gif?t=1675442150\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Trade goods with other planets to develop further</h2><br>To become sustainable, exchanging goods with other planets is necessary. Extract <strong>metals</strong> by building <strong>mines</strong>, transform them into <strong>goods</strong> in your <strong>factories</strong> and <strong>sell</strong> those via your <strong>market</strong>. You will then obtain more money to develop.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1813120/extras/market.gif?t=1675442150\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Be mindful of your actions</h2><br>Choose where you will build your 